  <description><![CDATA[<p>The iconic Grand Hotel Alassio boasts a prime position directly on the beachfront of this popular <a data-udi="umb://document/c0a1a2eb5f21493d858ec9013916a8fb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c0a1a2eb5f21493d858ec9013916a8fb}" title="Liguria">Ligurian</a> Town.</p>
<p>The stunning belle époque property sits proudly on Alassio’s seafront, just a short walk from the resorts many restaurants and shops. Directly outside the doors of the hotel, the gently sloping sandy beach is lined with comfortable loungers that belong to the hotel’s exclusive beach club. Spend lazy days enjoying the sounds of the calm water lapping the shore, or relax at the beach club’s bar where you can sample expertly made cocktails.</p>
<p>Taking advantage of its location, the hotel uses the nearby seawater in its impressive spa, which covers three floors and over 1,500 metres. The seawater pool boasts several jets and the spa offers a range of treatments from relaxing massages to detox programmes. There’s even treatments for teens.</p>
<p>The service at this five star retreat aims to make your stay as comfortable as possible. Enjoy fine dining at the Gazebo Restaurant, sundowners at the GH Bar and a wonderful kids’ club during summer that makes the hotel an ideal choice for both families and couples.</p>]]></description>
