  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Superior Rooms</strong> measure 22m² and enjoy windows with views of the mountains (sea view rooms are available for a supplement). Facilities include air conditioning, satellite TV, wifi, minibar and safe.</p>
<p><strong>Family Rooms</strong> are 30m² and have a double bed and a sofa bed. They enjoy mountain views.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Rooms</strong> are 25m² and enjoy a large, furnished terrace with superb sea views.</p>
<p><strong>Suites</strong> are available on request. Measuring 44m², they have a large living room, separate bedroom and a balcony with sea views.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
